{"tid":967579,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[小鳳姐]華為問責Twitter事故 相關責任人月薪扣5000","createTime":"2019-01-03T15:01:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-03T21:52:23.000Z","uid":66943,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"827da03111b7f30f8e2468b9dcd894bd439dd039","tid":967579,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T15:01:09.000Z","msg":"2018年12月31日晚間11點31分，華為官方Twitter以華為全體員工的名義送上新年祝福。不過，這篇推文下方卻留下了&ldquo;自Twitter的iPhone客戶端發出&rdquo;（Via Twitter for iPhone）的標記。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d6BMgyZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd6BMgyZ.jpg&h=0d0a7e16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n華為發出這條推文後立即將其刪除。不過，推文還是被 &ldquo;Marques Brownlee&rdquo;截圖，曝光後引發網友熱議。<br />\n<br />\n　　據梨視頻@老闆聯播官方微博消息，1月3日，華為簽發了關於華為官方Twitter賬號出現事故的問責決定。處罰文件稱，該貼文發布後，截圖出現在了部分海外和國內社交媒體上並廣泛傳播，該事件對華為手機的品牌帶來了不良影響。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t9Mz9Ua.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft9Mz9Ua.jpg&h=24b2dec6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其中，對直接責任人予以通報批評，個人職級降1級，月薪下調5000元。對數字營銷團隊主管予以通報批評，個人職級降級1級，月薪降5000元，年度考核不高於B。凍結個人職級晉升、漲薪，凍結期12個月，自2019年1月2日起計算。<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2aSjBzf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2aSjBzf.jpg&h=dcbb46b0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8f1d9e4772aba8b78c105db78bcc5bd1be7c43f1","tid":967579,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T15:04:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e349a4bcc47d7b0db1eeb4e404cb04de7ab39bd","tid":967579,"uid":123264,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T15:06:40.000Z","msg":"愛國是愛國 iph